01:19.356 --> 01:21.322
-Dad?
-We have a situation.

01:21.619 --> 01:23.619
Are you in there?

01:23.643 --> 01:26.513
Huh?
Can you see me?

01:27.018 --> 01:28.825
Can you see your son?

01:29.365 --> 01:31.341
