01:32.567 --> 01:34.095
You promised!

01:35.101 --> 01:36.711
Give me my life back!

02:48.602 --> 02:49.460
Ethan?

02:50.855 --> 02:51.678
Ethan...

02:52.905 --> 02:55.623
OK...Ethan, Ethan!

02:56.952 --> 02:58.079
Come on, say something.

02:59.489 --> 03:00.171
Come on...

03:00.908 --> 03:01.969
Who are you?

