Let me help you up.

03:10.070 --> 03:11.565
Let me help you up.

03:11.834 --> 03:12.625
Easy. You can do it.

03:12.650 --> 03:13.785
Easy...easy...careful, careful. Here.

03:13.821 --> 03:16.718
He's experiencing temporary
memory loss.

03:19.439 --> 03:20.894
He'll be OK.

03:21.681 --> 03:23.328
You know, I've been
meaning to ask you something.

03:25.041 --> 03:26.955
Was this ever about him?

03:28.369 --> 03:30.117
Or was it always just about you?

03:35.345 --> 03:36.728
Charles...

03:37.187 --> 03:38.633
He's your son.

03:38.657 --> 03:40.123
I'm well aware of that, Nick.

03:40.148 --> 03:41.428
